  "original_title": "\u0bae\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0ba8\u0b95\u0bb0 \u0b9a\u0baa\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1 \u0baa\u0ba3\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbe\u0bb3\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bbe\u0bb5\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0b9a\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0bc6\u0baf\u0bb2\u0b95\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0bae\u0bc1\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bcb\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bae\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Sanitation workers of Mannar City Council protest in front of District Secretariat",
      "author": "Vishnu",
      "body_lines": [
        "Mannar City Council's cleaners and drivers have taken out a vigil in front of the Mannar District Secretariat on the 4th of Monday morning.",
        "Waste disposal operations in the Mannar city area have been suspended for the past few days.",
        "Due to lack of proper supply of fuel, it is not possible to carry out the said waste disposal activities.",
        "The fuel needed for the vehicles is not properly provided for the cleaning work which is continuously being carried out by the Mannar City Council.",
        "At this stage, the Mannar City Council has been protesting to provide the necessary fuel for the purification work.",
        "The sanitation workers and drivers of the city council who participated in the protest carried banners with various slogans.",
        "Why are the health services of the local government councils downgraded? Why are the local government services neglected in the distribution of petrol? Do you not know that solid waste service is an essential service? They participated in the protest carrying banners with various slogans written on them.",
        "In this situation, Mannar District Government President Mrs. A. Sranli Dimel said that she will discuss with the protestors and take appropriate measures. At this stage, the protestors moved away from there."
      ],
